==========================================================================
DATA SOURCES
==========================================================================

This project uses data from:

1. SOHO/LASCO CME Catalogue (NASA/ESA)
   - Provided by NASA and ESA
   - Usage: CME parameters (V₀, ω)

2. DSCOVR Magnetometer & Plasma (NOAA/SWPC)
   - Provided by NOAA Space Weather Prediction Center
   - Usage: Real-time solar wind conditions

3. OMNI Heliospheric Dataset (NASA/GSFC)
   - Provided by NASA Goddard Space Flight Center
   - Usage: Historical validation data

4. GFZ Potsdam Kp Index
   - Provided by GFZ German Research Centre for Geosciences
   - Usage: Geomagnetic activity validation

5. NMDB Neutron Monitor Database
   - Provided by NMDB (http://www.nmdb.eu/)
   - Usage: Forbush decrease detection

